{"tid":105612,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"HDMI Switch推薦","createTime":"2017-02-03T04:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T07:07:41.000Z","uid":79724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55e8f05b6e7899ce329a46daeef045e2c680a572","tid":105612,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"請問有冇巴打可以推薦好用嘅HDMI Switch？<br />\n我需要2入1出，電腦 + PS4 Pro (HDCP 2.2) 全部出去一個1080P 60Hz螢光幕，係咪要注意個HDMI Swtich支援咩版本嘅HDCP？<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454c9669b1a716bffe6e9bf816ba8b8e3857fe3e","tid":105612,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cb4d70aadce7ad2201bc61ec625696c97a1757a","tid":105612,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"記住買獨立供電<br />\n<br />\n一年前買過<br />\n果陣d人推aten<br />\n<br />\n我係2&gt;1 所以買左個2&gt;1既<br />\n但唔包火牛要另外配<br />\n配撚完個價等如買個3&gt;1(包牛)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef8f829e3469b312d35194addab2bd225efe3ab","tid":105612,"uid":23890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記住買獨立供電<br />\n<br />\n一年前買過<br />\n果陣d人推aten<br />\n<br />\n我係2&gt;1 所以買左個2&gt;1既<br />\n但唔包火牛要另外配<br />\n配撚完個價等如買個3&gt;1(包牛)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾錢左右"},{"pid":"67b55d6ac52dcc1dd9b1197246d77cf4680aa974","tid":105612,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"去黃金地下有間鋪專賣SWITCH<br />\n幾好人<br />\n上次知我2入1出 提我比PS4要買有電版 唔係就用唔到"},{"pid":"77b87ae9c7d4945e9c346b5991ac7d6b8090d770","tid":105612,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記住買獨立供電<br />\n<br />\n一年前買過<br />\n果陣d人推aten<br />\n<br />\n我係2&amp;gt;1 所以買左個2&amp;gt;1既<br />\n但唔包火牛要另外配<br />\n配撚完個價等如買個3&amp;gt;1(包牛)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾錢左右</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7g3ukjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7g3ukjq.jpg&h=8457f95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩百零唔記得<br />\n原來係3&gt;1黎<br />\n<br />\n最記得係雖然唔插電都用到<br />\n但係如果冇插電<br />\n我果陣<br />\n1pc<br />\n2ps4<br />\n3無插<br />\n<br />\n你用佢粒制轉台就只能1去2去3去番1<br />\n但因為3冇插野=無電到<br />\n<br />\n卡撚住係3到<br />\n個遙控又虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迫住另外買火牛"},{"pid":"462f372b8dbb240781f1c477b3b8915653136fe6","tid":105612,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有想問audio係咪都pass through到隻switch<br />\n同埋用咗hdmi switch latency會唔會多好多<br />\n其實唔影響打機就ok"},{"pid":"8f634d430107d870d6e957249be410ad306b220d","tid":105612,"uid":30821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"一定要獨立供電果種，唔係打ps4會閃moon"},{"pid":"c966a2666161d20a91bb6e6c6957ba958a5a87bd","tid":105612,"uid":30821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有想問audio係咪都pass through到隻switch<br />\n同埋用咗hdmi switch latency會唔會多好多<br />\n其實唔影響打機就ok</blockquote><br />\n1,係 2,唔影響"},{"pid":"4e01d7cccb6f477b884d4dbce0dab7bfa174d4e0","tid":105612,"uid":5865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F15pcuM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF15pcuM.jpg&h=76fec107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊依隻"},{"pid":"7f8b0303d00bb71c266a4820abfaa3546995d26d","tid":105612,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"加條audio 線連住mon 個audio窿 同電腦底板既audio in <br />\n<br />\nset 一set sound card driver<br />\n就用到同一組喇叭 一齊出聲<br />\n但電腦要開住<br />\nps4先有聲"},{"pid":"2e12170c0818960dad4c80671dd2a9f80d004a65","tid":105612,"uid":2483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F15pcuM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF15pcuM.jpg&h=76fec107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊依隻</blockquote><br />\n+1 岩岩買左，但未用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa7ff3ee7cb612a7e521f2d78a463788ffe91c9","tid":105612,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"同你地相反，我買左1開2"},{"pid":"847854eba0015595f1b4f5b4bf955f64f2494b8c","tid":105612,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你地相反，我買左1開2</blockquote><br />\n一開二掉轉插=二開一"},{"pid":"a56bad4f9f72d4d0be5b29b3cac2ef961343fba3","tid":105612,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你地相反，我買左1開2</blockquote><br />\n一開二掉轉插=二開一</blockquote><br />\n我間房有電視同電腦mon，有時用電視玩有時用mon玩，廢事插黎插去"},{"pid":"ac648b0b4db43ef9e6b91f77bc30f85025997912","tid":105612,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你地相反，我買左1開2</blockquote><br />\n一開二掉轉插=二開一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前試過掉轉插係出唔到畫面<br />\n另外<br />\n1開2出係唔使禁嘢switch<br />\n長期都出畀兩邊畫面<br />\n<br />\n用緊1開2,再經4入2出matrix出幾個mon組合"},{"pid":"646a6951d7634777045554567fc32364c545b29d","tid":105612,"uid":8921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"我用aten vs481a，我買咗兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一個用咗一年多啲就燒火牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，隻火牛好罕見，行勻成個鴨寮街都揾唔到。<br />\n<br />\n第二個用咗年半到而家。<br />\n<br />\n不過撇開燒火牛唔計，呢個hdmi switch應該係最高質 (雖然都係最貴) 畫質無損，無lag，識自動跳去有信號嘅input，而且每個input channel都有獨立制，switch放得遠仲有㩒遙控轉channel，總之就係爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be4c13f324d81a00aeb5f328c2a950e8773d88","tid":105612,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用aten vs481a，我買咗兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一個用咗一年多啲就燒火牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，隻火牛好罕見，行勻成個鴨寮街都揾唔到。<br />\n<br />\n第二個用咗年半到而家。<br />\n<br />\n不過撇開燒火牛唔計，呢個hdmi switch應該係最高質 (雖然都係最貴) 畫質無損，無lag，識自動跳去有信號嘅input，而且每個input channel都有獨立制，switch放得遠仲有㩒遙控轉channel，總之就係爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買完上面果隻就後悔<br />\n雖然同牌子<br />\n比我揀我都係揀你呢隻"},{"pid":"619f19429d4d7fe82b90eb83626e1c3aa37dc009","tid":105612,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:36:40.000Z","msg":"用緊3 to 1 無獨立供電都無問題<br />\n1 ps4<br />\n2 電腦<br />\n3 micro hidi 連tablet<br />\n都係雜嘜牌"},{"pid":"a3db56d80ab58620a449eb3ca6433c51efa25779","tid":105612,"uid":48899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"高質post 留名<br />\n一個switch 解決好多問題 <br />\n太多HDMI 線 駁嚟駁去<br />\n用唔同機又要轉台"},{"pid":"82892042c3b13fcd81a92755aa238a9531a8699f","tid":105612,"uid":88,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"點解要咁貴既switch?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用緊個d 垃圾一開三 幾廿蚊隻個d <br />\n一樣用係pc ps4 同一個空左<br />\n都無lag 無閃 同識自己有訊號就轉input<br />\n有聲 又唔會卡係空左個格到wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63e8adef57256bf724356ce39edcb3b98682f59","tid":105612,"uid":37097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要咁貴既switch?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用緊個d 垃圾一開三 幾廿蚊隻個d <br />\n一樣用係pc ps4 同一個空左<br />\n都無lag 無閃 同識自己有訊號就轉input<br />\n有聲 又唔會卡係空左個格到wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你電腦個hdmi port 比左電個switch , 所以冇事<br />\n<br />\n卡係空位似個switch 有問題多d, 我隻兩隻aten 唔插電都唔會咁"},{"pid":"510532a5bf72fbb350f7cc766c359a906d26c6c6","tid":105612,"uid":1042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=42593116255&amp;spm=a1z09.2.0.0.JvK3Rh&amp;_u=4bvhg792dfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fid%3D42593116255%26spm%3Da1z09.2.0.0.JvK3Rh%26_u%3D4bvhg792dfc&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=aba75c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=42593116255&amp;spm=a1z09.2.0.0.JvK3Rh&amp;_u=4bvhg792dfc</a><br />\n喺淘寶買咗呢隻"},{"pid":"638fb71ec8c1dd96a99596bd7a9cc2311001fe70","tid":105612,"uid":88,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解要咁貴既switch?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用緊個d 垃圾一開三 幾廿蚊隻個d <br />\n一樣用係pc ps4 同一個空左<br />\n都無lag 無閃 同識自己有訊號就轉input<br />\n有聲 又唔會卡係空左個格到wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你電腦個hdmi port 比左電個switch , 所以冇事<br />\n<br />\n卡係空位似個switch 有問題多d, 我隻兩隻aten 唔插電都唔會咁</blockquote><br />\n咁同貴個d switch 有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}